Overall, these results demonstrate that Neon---augmented with in-context examples---is capable of rivaling the performance of a live web-scale search engine for temporal entity-centric QA. Additionally, the individual strengths of the different approaches suggest a hybrid system that can leverage them jointly for even better performance; we leave such explorations to future work.